locality: Llanganati. Paramo SE of Chosa Aucacocha, between Aucacocha and Pan de Azucar. Hilly paramo, dominated by 1-2 m high Neurolepis scrub, scattered Escallonia and Gynoxys, and Oritrophium swamps. Soil temperature 6.5° C.
